author: Anjana George
title: 'Muthugau' will have four unique songs
text:
Suresh Gopi's son, Gokul Suresh, starrer film, Muthugau will have four songs composed by Rahul Raj which include a romantic melody
Director Vipin Das's debut venture Muthugau that casts Gokul Suresh will have four songs-a romantic melody, a folk song, a peppy number and a surprise one! The music is composed by Rahul Raj.
